    "body": "## Purpose\n\nCreative/product foundation for Stage 6 Step 9 before Codex implementation.\n\nThis PR remains deliberately **draft** and **documentation/data only**. It does not modify runtime/game code and is not frozen implementation authority.\n\n## Authority\n\nBaseline main: `7673f3487b0dd52c0c5cb2c7826f4e3fe5cc570e`.\n\nTarget profiles: `RU_BOOMER / RU_GEN_X / RU_MILLENNIAL / RU_ZOOMER / RU_ALPHA`.\n\nRule: `NO FALSE OR MISUSED SLANG`, not `NO SLANG`. Russian cultural lanes must not be produced by translating or mixing foreign generational culture.\n\n## Completed foundation step\n\n### ✅ 1. FULL_ALPHA_RUSSIAN_FIRST_REWRITE\n\nExecuted as a complete current-foundation rewrite overlay:\n\n- `STAGE6_STEP9_ALPHA_RUSSIAN_FIRST_REWRITE_V1.md`\n- `stage6_step9_alpha_ru_rewrite_v1.json`\n- `STAGE6_STEP9_ALPHA_RUSSIAN_FIRST_CORRECTION.md` updated to `STEP1_REWRITE_PASS_EXECUTED`\n\nThe pass supersedes conflicting English-heavy Alpha copy in Batch 1-4, onboarding, NPC pools and voice-bible examples.\n\nKey corrections:\n- I0/I1 are Russian-first and immediately understandable;\n- broad `start/rules/checking/joined/event forced/pay up/...` English fallback removed;\n- selective `W/L`, `NPC`, `аура`, `cooked`, `mid`, `skill issue`, `репорт`, `ивент`, `КД`, etc. remain only where semantically and culturally natural;\n- `fanum tax` generic robbery misuse removed;\n- canonical REP/economy/mechanic meanings remain explicit and are not silently renamed to meme vocabulary;\n- Alpha NPC pools rewritten Russian-first;\n- unresolved mechanic/source rows remain blocked instead of guessed.\n\nStep 1 is complete **as a creative draft rewrite pass**, not frozen/approved implementation copy.\n\n## Structural findings retained\n\n- Gen X partial plumbing exists but is not first-class.\n- Historical seed core: `Zoomer == Alpha` on `57/57` resolved keys; `Boomer == Millennial` on `19/57`.\n- Seed inventory is historical only: 1930 active records / 853 unique texts / 306 dynamic templates; fresh current-main inventory is still required before freeze.\n- PR #258 unified stat-toast architecture must remain.\n\n## Current diff\n\nBranch: `chatgpt/stage6-step9-five-profile-foundation-20260723`\n\nCurrent head: `761b1d1c93909186e9cef5757c302f4060c0c79d`\n\nCompared with baseline main:\n- 20 commits ahead\n- 0 behind\n- 19 documentation/data files\n- 0 runtime/game files changed\n\n## Status\n\n`STAGE 6: NOT COMPLETE`\n\n`STEP 9: FOUNDATION_IN_PROGRESS / NOT_FROZEN`\n\nChecklist:\n- [x] 1. FULL_ALPHA_RUSSIAN_FIRST_REWRITE\n- [ ] 2. RU_CULTURAL_AUTHENTICITY_PASS B/X/M/Z/A\n- [ ] 3. FRESH_CURRENT_MAIN_INVENTORY\n- [ ] 4. GAP_CLOSURE\n- [ ] 5. USER_REVIEW\n- [ ] 6. FREEZE + SHA256\n- [ ] 7. CODEX IMPLEMENTATION\n\nNext action: `RU_CULTURAL_AUTHENTICITY_PASS_ALL_FIVE_COLUMNS`.",
